CatDescriptText: Cutline for related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A32, reads: "Little League Dodgers - Coach C. Bolden and Manager Curtis are standing behind their Dodgers, as the youngsters attempt to become solid nine.  Front rom [sic], from left: F. Grant, D. Phillips, C. Upshur, G. Dacton and C. Lindsay.  Second row: R. Butler, I. Johnson, W. Lee, F. Hill, L. Duncan, B. Simpson, T. Sumpter and A. White. - Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Dodgers Little League baseball team, first row from left: F. Grant, D. Phillips, C. Upshur, G. Dacton, C. Lindsay; second row: R. Butler, I. Johnson, W. Lee, F. Hill, L. Duncan, B. Simpson, T. Sumpter, A. White; rear: Coach C. Bolden and Manager Curtis, posed on field
